readable.content: A dog is carrying a red toy in its mouth running in a field of brown grass next to a second dog . Two brown dogs running through a field with a red toy Two brown dogs run side by side and one dog is carrying an orange container in its mouth . Two brown dogs wearing orange collars are running through some tall grass , one carrying an orange item . Two greyish brown dogs play with an orange toy .
